htmail-view (0.2) unstable; urgency=low

  * Add accelerator keys:
    - q: quit htmail-view
    - r: toggle remote resources
  * Add getopts handling.
  * Add verbose mode.
  * Add wmctrl wrapper (focus handling).
  * Ignore policy requests not triggered by link-clicked.
  * Improve window handling:
    - bring to front on start
    - set reasonable title
    - show destinitations of links
    - use a standard icon
  * Rename project to htmail-view.

 -- Thomas Liske <thomas@fiasko-nw.net>  Sun, 27 Sep 2015 11:58:45 +0200

